# Rules

- No emojis e.g. 😀 of any kind
- No semicolons e.g. ; in responses (code is exempt)
- Always use plain ASCII no Unicode. Eg no em/en dash.
- Follow YAGNI principles, and one-liner solutions.
- In markdown files always add a newline `\n` after a `.` instead of making a very long single line.
- If you run into a token issue dont try and get around it ask the user.
